data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in Old Mill Basin! This stunning, recently renovated single-family home is a true gem, offering both elegance and modern convenience. Boasting a detached structure, this residence provides the privacy and space you've been searching for.
This home features 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 full baths, ensuring ample space for your family or guests. The enormous living room and formal dining room are perfect for entertaining, adorned with parquet hardwood floors that add a touch of sophistication to the interior.
The heart of the home lies in the renovated eat-in kitchen, complete with modern amenities and direct access to a backyard oasis. Step outside to a patio, where you can unwind and enjoy the tranquility of your private outdoor space.
One of the standout features of this property is the convenience of private parking. Your very own driveway accommodates several cars, supplemented by a detached garage for added storage or parking needs. The finished basement, with a separate entrance, adds versatility to the space and can be utilized as a guest suite, home office, or recreation area.
Situated in Old Mill Basin, this home is surrounded by amenities. Explore nearby restaurants and shopping along Avenue N, and enjoy easy access to transportation options, including B41, B46-B46 SBS, B47, and B100 buses along Utica Avenue. Families will appreciate the proximity to P.S. 203 and P.S. 326, adding convenience to daily routines.
Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your home sweet home. Hurry, it's a must-see!
